reviews.reviewText: I was hesitant about getting it, however it has been a great deal for its price. The clothes are almost dry by the end of the cycle and it washes really well. reviews.reviewText: I’m soo very glad I decided to purchase this washing machine. So far, it has been a godsend.. thoroughly washing my clothes. I haven’t had any issues. It was so easy to assemble and very easy to use. I’d definitely recommend to anyone looking for a washing machine of this kind.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 6, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Top 3 Best Purchase of All Time
reviews.reviewText: What can I say? I can’t believe I didn’t get this sooner. Almost 3 years of living in an apartment, having to get coins constantly and wasting money on 100 year old dirty machines.This thing has changed my life!!! It has all the functions you would ever need. Even “childlock” which is coming in handy—my cat kept pushing the buttons and ending the cycle, lol.My tips:-have someone handy in order to do the sink hookup. I purchased a separate sink attachment on amazon so I can switch from sink/laundry easily. My dad also purchased me a new hose and stuff but that’s not totally necessary. When I initially was trying to do the sink hookup on my own (just with the products that came with it), water was spraying out of my faucet. Really recommend having someone handy help the initial setup.-do not use laundry pods. Suds were boiling over every time and items were coming out stiff. I use 1/2 TBSP of HE detergent and it’s been going better.-get a dolly (on amazon) to prop it up and easily move it when not using.-SECURE the drainage hose. I used a hair tie and a butterfly clip.-do an extra spin cycle to dry the clothes even more. You can also do the “tub dry” which is a 30 min spin cylce.I absolutely love being able to do laundry right in the convenience of my own home!
